      <rules>
        <rule name="Cloak &amp; Dagger" id="36fc-bb5c-2cfb-8578" hidden="false">
          <description>Duellists are adept at fighting using their billowing cloaks to swirl at an enemy distracting him and warding off blows.


The Duellist counts as using a shield in close combat.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule name="Wall of Steel" id="c217-4cbc-943f-77a5" hidden="false">
          <description>Even the most lowly of Ashigaru is a veteran of hours of drill, and because of this If wielding a spear you may choose to wield it twohanded, in which case the spear gains the parry special rule</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
    </selectionEntry>
