      <rules>
        <rule name="Wardens of the Castle" id="f972-f1fa-0e32-de65" hidden="false">
          <description>Traditionally responsible for the defense of the homeland while the men are at war, the Onnabushi have gained a gruesome reputation for urban warfare, while inside buildings or ruins., then gain the fear ability. It&apos;s a good idea to define which bits of your terrain collection count as &apos;buildings or ruins&apos; at the start of a battle to avoid confusion later.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
